text: Bård Magnus Nesteng (born 14 May 1979, in Fredrikstad, Norway) is a Norwegian archer. Nesteng competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics, 2012 Summer Olympics, and the 2016 Summer Olympics.Bård NestengBaard NESTENG == References == Category:Norwegian archers Category:Olympians for Norway Category:1979 births Category:Living people
